dc_title_s: Mills County, Iowa, 1960, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol BKI. Form of individual image numbering: BKI-1AA-[number], or BKI-2AA-[number]."Flying completed 7-30-60""Approximate scale, 1:20,000" [refers to individual images from which mosaic was made].
